WEBVTT

03:42.303 --> 03:44.837
You have so many now Sahaja Yogis, ah?

03:45.463 --> 03:48.304
The interpreter: “Yes, Shri Mataji. They are all Sahaja Yogis”

03:48.518 --> 03:49.523
So many!

03:49.590 --> 03:51.058
The interpreter: “Yes, Shri Mataji”.

06:04.206 --> 06:06.832
I’m amazed to see so many

06:06.857 --> 06:09.380
Sahaja Yogis in Ukraine.

06:23.582 --> 06:25.384
That shows how people are

06:25.409 --> 06:27.973
sensitive to spirituality,

06:31.815 --> 06:35.139
that they are taking to it so easily.

06:39.046 --> 06:40.927
They have been waiting I think,

06:40.952 --> 06:43.253
seeking all these years

06:43.396 --> 06:46.149
and suddenly now they have found the way.

07:02.564 --> 07:04.833
I see your love and

07:04.924 --> 07:08.905
your compassionment, your sweetness.

07:09.249 --> 07:13.440
I just don’t know how to put it in words – what I feel.

07:29.368 --> 07:32.375
Tonight for the Program I hope you’ll be all there

07:32.599 --> 07:34.743
and I’ll tell you

07:35.045 --> 07:38.637
how to be with yourself

07:38.662 --> 07:41.930
and how to be with everybody else.

07:51.409 --> 07:54.123
We have to bring peace to this world.

07:57.060 --> 07:59.014
And you people can do it.

08:01.359 --> 08:04.391
And the way it is spreading here

08:04.550 --> 08:07.081
it has to spread all over the world.

08:12.684 --> 08:16.431
There are some very nice girls married from here

08:16.487 --> 08:17.709
– from Kyiv.

08:23.490 --> 08:26.355
And they have a very-very

08:27.386 --> 08:31.162
good reports about them.

08:36.400 --> 08:39.300
Also about the men who were married.

08:43.030 --> 08:44.903
They say that they are very deep,

08:44.928 --> 08:47.760
very great Sahaja Yogis.

08:52.341 --> 08:55.084
Specially in America

08:55.402 --> 08:58.219
they are very much adored.

09:05.705 --> 09:07.872
And they can’t understand

09:08.047 --> 09:11.666
how Russians have been so

09:12.096 --> 09:15.097
great in spirituality.

09:19.961 --> 09:23.429
Speci - about the Ukraine people also

09:23.501 --> 09:26.395
when I’ll tell them they’ll be amazed.

09:31.851 --> 09:35.762
They ask Me, “Why Russia and Ukraine, why?”

09:36.985 --> 09:38.972
I don’t know what to answer.

09:44.667 --> 09:47.153
You’ll have to tell Me the answer.

09:56.373 --> 09:59.333
I thank you to come all the way

09:59.612 --> 10:01.468
to this airport

10:02.374 --> 10:04.053
to welcome Me.

10:05.001 --> 10:08.022
My heart is filled

10:08.206 --> 10:11.230
with tremendous happiness.

10:21.600 --> 10:24.171
You can understand what a mother feels

10:24.215 --> 10:27.624
when she meets her children after such a long time.

10:36.585 --> 10:40.445
So I hope you all will come now

10:40.842 --> 10:44.508
to the Program and we have to expand Sahaja Yoga

10:51.524 --> 10:54.677
to give love, wisdom

10:54.844 --> 10:57.308
and joy to others.

11:01.552 --> 11:02.770
Thank you.

17:04.009 --> 17:08.017
Say that you must take for a longer period in this country

17:08.042 --> 17:12.579
so that the problems of the Ukraine people will be solved. Please say it.

17:28.770 --> 17:30.770
Shri Mataji: he speaks good Russian

17:55.556 --> 18:00.555
Indians are saying that, “You should stay here for a longer period.”

18:02.540 --> 18:05.080
They are all requesting Me I should stay here

18:05.105 --> 18:08.651
for a longer period to solve the problem of the people.

18:30.908 --> 18:33.447
Indians report there are problems.

19:19.089 --> 19:20.660
Thank you very much.

